00:27:02,673 --> 00:27:04,574
But since there's this whole question of is she crazy

557
00:27:04,654 --> 00:27:06,374
or is she not throughout the story,

558
00:27:06,914 --> 00:27:09,055
it was a really nice thematic overlay

559
00:27:11,435 --> 00:27:14,456
with puzzles and stuff, but it basically showed me

560
00:27:14,476 --> 00:27:16,176
they'd sort of learned something from their play through

561
00:27:16,236 --> 00:27:19,477
of Gone Home as far as like how to physically tell a story,

562
00:27:20,237 --> 00:27:21,717
but in a much more subtle way,

563
00:27:22,017 --> 00:27:23,177
even though what they were really doing here

564
00:27:23,197 --> 00:27:24,818
was sort of puzzle making.

